&lt;br&gt; | &lt;b&gt;Objectives of the Project&lt;/b&gt;:

The Project aims at developing the agricultural production in Iwanda Agricultural Development area situated in the southern part of the country and thereby facilitate the transport of the agricultural production to the consumption and export areas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Components of the Project&lt;/b&gt;:

The Project consists of the construction of 143 kilometers long road of two lanes with width of 6.7 meter and shoulders of 1.5 meter each. The Project includes pavement layers, water drainage facilities, slope protection, road safety works, feeder roads, layover and crossings and parking areas, in addition to institutional support for the Road Department.&lt;/div&gt;
